{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864614106,"sessionID":"ses_28638dbeaffeVawnyVVR7h7E8m","part":{"id":"prt_d79c76ffb001Cbx9E50Xrcb22l","messageID":"msg_d79c76297001Og1zM9Mdj2vuG6","sessionID":"ses_28638dbeaffeVawnyVVR7h7E8m","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_5198afc36810426b9633f3a4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-024 — DockerService 封装\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the DockerService encapsulation in the AgentCube CLI tool (`kubectl-agentcube`).\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-024\n- **Module**: `cmd/cli`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n(TODO: Describe the background and motivation for DockerService encapsulation)\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### AR-024-001: (TBD)\n\n#### Scenario: AR-024-001-A — (TBD)\n\n- **GIVEN** \n- **WHEN** \n- **THEN** \n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC001: \n\n---\n\n## Architecture Notes\n\n### Key Components\n\n| Component | Path | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| (TBD) | | |\n\n### (TBD) Flow\n\n```\n```\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Related: AR-023 (invoke/status command)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775864614094,"end":1775864614105}}}}
